== Stovetop ==

Bring 4 cups water to a boil in a medium #pot{}.

Add @Omsom Soy Garlic Saucy Noodles{1} and cook to desired doneness, ~{4%minutes}. Drain noodles and return to #pot.

Add @Omsom Coconut Lemongrass Curry Saucy Noodles{1} and stir to combine. Enjoy!

== Microwave ==

Add @Omsom Soy Garlic Saucy Noodles{1} and 2 cups water to a large #microwave-safe bowl{}.

Microwave for ~{3%minutes}; stir to separate. Microwave until noodles reach desired doneness, ~{3%minutes} more. Drain noodles and return to #bowl.

Add @Omsom Coconut Lemongrass Curry Saucy Noodles{1} and stir to combine. Enjoy!

> Cook times may vary slightly - adjust to your microwave.

== Kettle ==

Bring water to a boil in a #kettle{}.

Combine @Omsom Soy Garlic Saucy Noodles{1} and 2 cups boiling water in a large heatproof #bowl{}. Cover bowl and let sit until noodles reach desired doneness, ~{6%minutes}. Drain noodles and return to bowl.

Add @Omsom Coconut Lemongrass Curry Saucy Noodles{1} and stir to combine. Enjoy!
